Wolfblade::

She smiled as he started to pull her away from the main entrance. She
giggled slightly, which made her feel funny since she never giggles.
"What are you doing?" she said with a chuckle. "Where are you trying
take me?"  She gently tugged back, but he was stronger than she was
and so she gave in. "OK, OK, what it is?" she said with a sweet,
loving smile on her face plates.
